{"title":"「FJSC2018PJD8T4」石子合并","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":256,"tags":[],"operation":{"submit":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/problem/5088#submit_code","submissions":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/submissions?problem_id=5088","statistics":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/problem/5088/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/problem/5088/testdata","discussion":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/discussion/problem/5088"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"在一个操场上一排地摆放着 $N$ 堆石子。现要将石子有次序地合并成一堆。 规定每次只能选相邻的 $2$ 堆石子合并成新的一堆，并将新的一堆石子数记为 该次合并的得分。 \r\n\n\r\n\n试设计一个程序，计算出将 $N$ 堆石子合并成一堆的最小得分。  "},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"从文件`unite.in`读入\r\n\n\r\n\n第一行为一个正整数 $N$，以下 $N$ 行，每行一个正整数，分别表示第 $i$ 堆石子的个数。  "},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"输出到文件`unite.out`\r\n\n\r\n\n为一个正整数，即最小得分。 "},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"### 输入样例1\r\n\r\n``` plain\r\n7\r\n13\r\n7\r\n8\r\n16\r\n21\r\n4\r\n18 \r\n```\r\n\r\n### 输出样例1\r\n\r\n``` plain\r\n239\r\n```"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"$2 \\le N \\le 100$，石堆中石子的个数$\\leq 10000$"}]}